The Nuborn Project is a new project of electronic music, more specifically, Electro House.
The tracks follow a line of strong and deep bass, loops and characteristic of electro and dance and explosive sounds well and influenced by artists such as Deadmau5, Benny Benassi, Felguk, David Guetta and Bruno Barudi. The Nuborn Project is a project currently formed by DJ and producer in Brazil Isaias Vasconcelos.
The Dj Sets range from Electro House, Prog House, or House, with a refined technique of mixing that ensures continuity of the dance floor.
Enjoy this beautiful work !!!!!
